member.name: M:Blackbaud.AppFx.WebAPI.DataFormServices.GetFormData``1(Blackbaud.AppFx.WebAPI.AppFxWebServiceProvider,Blackbaud.AppFx.WebAPI.ServiceProxy.DataFormLoadRequest)
member.summary: Calls DataFormLoad using the supplied AppFxWebServiceProvider and DataFormLoadRequest
member.typeparam: A class that inherits from Blackbaud.AppFx.WebAPI.FormData. The class must override the SetValuesFromDataFormItem method.
member.param: The AppFxWebServiceProvider to use to issue the DataFormLoadRequest
The DataFormLoadRequest that has been initialized with the parameters to use for the web service call
member.returns: An instance of the FormData class that has been initialized with the results of the DataFormLoadRequest
member.remarks: A class which uses this function must override the SetValuesFromDataFormItem method and in that method load the values from the supplied DataFormItem. This function is useful for code generated by tools such as BBMetalWeb.exe

member.name: P:Blackbaud.AppFx.WebAPI.AppFxWebServiceProvider.AutoDisableNagleAlgorithm
member.summary: Controls wether the provider will automatically disable the Nagle algorithm for then service url.
member.remarks: In most cases it is best to set the service point UseNagleAlgorithm to false for the web service endpoint. By default the AppFxWebServiceProvider will set UseNagleAlgorithm to False on the System.Net.ServicePoint for the given url. Setting this property to False will disable this automatic behavior.
